snippet.textDisplay: This is not the kind of music I listen to (i'm into mostly electronic music) and I'm fiercely proud of Coke Studio Pakistan (my home country after all) but this was excellent. Well produced, had such a lively groove and beautiful fusion of performers. Neha Kakkar and Kamla Devi stole the show! What a class production through and through. Much love from Pakistan. Looking forward to all the releases from your new season!
